      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nin general, I think it's incorrect to process deleted objects. Ideally, we should enqueue a lock first, then lookup the object, but this is not the case now. so, I'd think we can check the object still does exist once ldlm lock is granted.",
