      "date": "2014-05-26 05:32:47.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/db0d7780-e496-11e3-b362-52540035b04c).  Ran 8 tests.  No failures.",
